{"tid":1274712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"即興旅行好地方","createTime":"2019-07-01T17:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T17:08:59.000Z","uid":125210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"06dfee5379f6dafe1ed2c82e4a890dc25390a6d8","tid":1274712,"uid":125210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"最快最低價：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">台灣</span>可以即時上網買<br />\n入台證香港人即申請即批，去機場叫地勤/lounge幫你print<br />\n<a href=\"https://niioa.immigration.gov.tw/NIA_OnlineApply_inter/visafreeApply/visafreeApplyForm.action\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fniioa.immigration.gov.tw%2FNIA_OnlineApply_inter%2FvisafreeApply%2FvisafreeApplyForm.action&d=qB%2BEr1lTQcBPVU2CyFsNoi3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=10d127c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://niioa.immigration.gov.tw/NIA_OnlineApply_inter/visafreeApply/visafreeApplyForm.action</a><br />\n太趕而去過可以落地簽，但要用台幣即時比錢<br />\n<br />\n最安全：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">德國</span><br />\n德國人友善好客<br />\n德國腸都好食啊"}]}